01:15:09.510 --> 01:15:11.679
? That'll make you move
your body down to the ground

01:15:11.762 --> 01:15:16.266
? We got Poindexter on the violin
And Lewis and Gilbert will be joinin' in

01:15:16.350 --> 01:15:20.854
? We got Booger Presley on a mean guitar
And a rap by little old me, Lamar

01:15:20.938 --> 01:15:23.482
? We got Takashi beating on his gong

01:15:23.565 --> 01:15:25.693
? The boys and the Mus are clappin' along

01:15:25.776 --> 01:15:28.028
? And just when you thought you'd seen it all

01:15:28.112 --> 01:15:30.322
? Along comes a Lambda four foot tall

01:15:30.406 --> 01:15:32.533
? So, Wormser, come on out here on the floor

01:15:32.616 --> 01:15:34.952
? So we can work our bodies
like never before

01:15:35.035 --> 01:15:37.871
? Break

01:16:08.152 --> 01:16:10.738
(wild cheering and applause)

01:16:30.132 --> 01:16:34.511
I'd like to present the trophy
to this year's champions,

01:16:34.595 --> 01:16:37.514
Lambda Lambda Lambda and Omega Mu.

01:16:43.187 --> 01:16:48.942
They will be able to select the president
of next year's Greek Council.

01:16:51.945 --> 01:16:57.493
I'd like to announce we've made
our selection already. It's Gilbert Lowe!

01:17:01.413 --> 01:17:05.250
This sucks! I gotta get rid of this anger.
C'mon, Betty, let's pump iron.

01:17:05.334 --> 01:17:07.878
No, Stan. I don't think so.

01:17:07.961 --> 01:17:11.673
What d'you mean, you don't think so?
C'mon, let's go. Why not?

01:17:11.757 --> 01:17:14.927
I've got a date with a Tri-Lamb.

01:17:15.010 --> 01:17:17.596
- A Tri-Lamb!
- Here's your pin.

01:17:19.640 --> 01:17:21.642
Take it.

01:17:21.725 --> 01:17:23.936
Wait. Betty...

01:17:24.019 --> 01:17:25.646
C'mon.

01:17:26.563 --> 01:17:29.191
God! I'm in love with a nerd!

01:17:30.901 --> 01:17:33.821
- Gable.
- Yeah, Coach.

01:17:33.904 --> 01:17:39.493
I wanna see you and the other girls
in the locker room now!

01:17:40.285 --> 01:17:41.787
Yes, sir.

01:17:48.961 --> 01:17:52.506
You know, when you were
a baby in your crib,

01:17:52.589 --> 01:17:56.802
your father looked down at you,
he had but one hope -

01:17:57.428 --> 01:18:00.180
"Someday my son will grow to be a man."

01:18:02.057 --> 01:18:04.601
Well, look at you now.

01:18:06.270 --> 01:18:12.735
You just got your asses whipped
by a bunch of goddamn nerds.

01:18:15.070 --> 01:18:17.239
Nerds!

01:18:19.366 --> 01:18:22.494
Well, if I was you, I'd do something about it.

01:18:24.246 --> 01:18:27.374
I would get up and redeem myself

01:18:28.459 --> 01:18:32.671
in the eyes of my father,
my Maker and my coach!

01:18:32.755 --> 01:18:35.507
- Let's get those nerds!
- Nerds!

01:18:35.591 --> 01:18:37.092
Nerds!

01:18:37.176 --> 01:18:39.595
What are we waitin' for?!

01:18:47.394 --> 01:18:52.191
? We're Lambda Lambda Lambda
and Omega Mu

01:18:52.274 --> 01:18:55.402
(chanting) Nerds! Nerds! Nerds! Nerds!

01:19:03.035 --> 01:19:04.995
(Stan) Come on!

01:19:05.079 --> 01:19:07.748
Come on!

01:19:35.484 --> 01:19:37.569
I'm a nerd.

01:19:38.946 --> 01:19:41.615
Welcome to the real world.

01:19:41.699 --> 01:19:44.535
I never really wanted to believe that.

01:19:44.618 --> 01:19:47.329
- It's OK.
- It's not OK.

01:19:47.413 --> 01:19:49.998
We're nothing.

01:19:50.082 --> 01:19:52.459
We let them destroy our house.

01:19:52.543 --> 01:19:56.213
- We'll control the Greek Council next year.
- Big deal!

01:19:57.756 --> 01:20:00.926
You'll be dead by then, Gilbert.

01:20:01.010 --> 01:20:05.305
Nobody cares. Don't you understand that?
The university doesn't care.

01:20:05.389 --> 01:20:07.975
There's nothin' we can do about it.

01:20:08.058 --> 01:20:11.770
We got something good goin',
and I won't let 'em take it away from us.

01:20:11.854 --> 01:20:16.066
Gilbert, don't be a fool.
You'll just get yourself hurt again.

01:20:16.150 --> 01:20:18.777
- Big deal.
- Gilbert?

01:20:24.533 --> 01:20:27.119
(? Brass band plays marching tune)

01:20:40.090 --> 01:20:43.886
I'd like to introduce the men
that will bring you a homecoming victory

01:20:43.969 --> 01:20:46.513
against State tomorrow.

01:20:46.597 --> 01:20:49.391
At defensive back,
number 38, Kevin O'Leary.

01:20:51.143 --> 01:20:54.688
Offensive guard,
number 64, Rich Valrow.

01:20:56.065 --> 01:20:59.568
At centre,
number 53, Harry Reagan.

01:21:01.570 --> 01:21:03.864
- Look who's comin'.
- Where you goin'?

01:21:03.947 --> 01:21:07.493
You went way too far this time,
and you're not gettin' away with it.

01:21:07.576 --> 01:21:12.456
Oh, is that right? Well, let's see if shit floats.
What do you think of that idea?

01:21:12.539 --> 01:21:15.959
Come on! Put me down!
Goddamn! Put me down!

01:21:16.043 --> 01:21:19.088
(Stan) Fire away!

01:21:19.171 --> 01:21:21.507
Now our tri-captains.

01:21:22.424 --> 01:21:27.638
Leading the conference in reception,
at wide receiver, number 84, Danny Burke.

01:21:28.013 --> 01:21:33.477
Our defensive captain,
number 79, Fred Polowoski - the Ogre.

01:21:35.062 --> 01:21:40.776
Now our two-time all-American quarterback,
number ten, Stan Gable.

01:21:45.823 --> 01:21:48.659
Hold it, son. Hold it, hold it!

01:21:48.742 --> 01:21:51.370
Leave him alone.
Coach, I said leave him alone.

01:21:51.453 --> 01:21:54.540
What did you say?
I'll break his goddamn neck.

01:21:54.623 --> 01:21:58.210
You will do nothing of the sort.
Don't touch that boy.

01:22:02.131 --> 01:22:04.383
Says who?

01:22:05.467 --> 01:22:09.513
Says me... you asshole.

01:22:10.556 --> 01:22:14.560
Hold it, Coach.
You just hold it right there.

01:22:50.429 --> 01:22:52.514
OK, kid.

01:22:53.849 --> 01:22:56.477
Say what you gotta say.

01:22:56.560 --> 01:22:58.437
Thanks.

01:23:04.485 --> 01:23:10.699
Uh... I just wanted to say that...
that I'm a nerd.

01:23:11.617 --> 01:23:15.996
And I'm here tonight to stand up
for the rights of other nerds.

01:23:16.080 --> 01:23:20.501
I mean, all our lives we've been laughed at

01:23:20.584 --> 01:23:23.462
and made to feel inferior.

01:23:23.545 --> 01:23:29.593
And tonight those bastards,
they trashed our house.

01:23:30.594 --> 01:23:32.304
Why?

01:23:32.388 --> 01:23:35.140
Because we're smart?

01:23:35.224 --> 01:23:38.060
Because we look different?

01:23:38.143 --> 01:23:40.771
Well, we're not.

01:23:41.939 --> 01:23:46.360
I'm a nerd, and... I'm pretty proud of it.

01:23:52.783 --> 01:23:54.660
Hi, Gilbert.

01:23:55.536 --> 01:23:57.746
I'm a nerd, too.

01:23:58.789 --> 01:24:01.583
I just found that out tonight.

01:24:01.667 --> 01:24:04.211
We have news for the beautiful people.

01:24:04.294 --> 01:24:08.173
There's a lot more of us than there are of you.

01:24:08.716 --> 01:24:10.926
I know there's alumni here tonight.

01:24:11.010 --> 01:24:16.056
When you went to Adams,
you might have been called a spaz,

01:24:16.515 --> 01:24:20.310
or a dork, or a geek.

01:24:20.394 --> 01:24:23.063
Any of you that have ever felt...

01:24:23.147 --> 01:24:27.443
stepped on, left out, picked on, put down,

01:24:28.360 --> 01:24:32.197
whether you think you're a nerd or not,
why don't you come and join us?

01:24:32.281 --> 01:24:33.782
Come on.

01:24:36.160 --> 01:24:40.080
(? "We are the Champions" by Queen)

01:24:40.164 --> 01:24:41.665
- Hi, Betty.
- Hi.

01:24:41.749 --> 01:24:44.376
Just join us, cos, uh...

01:24:44.460 --> 01:24:45.961
Hi.

01:24:47.087 --> 01:24:50.841
(Gilbert) No one's really gonna be free
until nerd persecution ends.

01:25:22.623 --> 01:25:27.711
You know, Coach, I think I'm gonna let
these boys live over at the Alpha Beta house,

01:25:27.795 --> 01:25:30.673
while you and your boys rebuild theirs.

01:25:30.756 --> 01:25:34.301
- And where the hell are we gonna live?
- What about us, huh?

01:25:35.052 --> 01:25:37.388
You're jocks, go live in the gym.

01:25:38.889 --> 01:25:41.725
(all, softly) Nerd. Nerd. Nerd.

01:25:41.809 --> 01:25:44.395
(all chant loudly) Nerd! Nerd! Nerd!

01:25:44.478 --> 01:25:46.897
Nerd! Nerd! Nerd! Nerd!

01:25:53.320 --> 01:25:55.406
(cheering)

01:26:04.915 --> 01:26:08.043
(? "We are the Champions" choral version)

01:27:27.748 --> 01:27:30.876
(? "They're So Incredible" by Revenge)

